Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 龙咲海 与狮堂光、凤凰寺风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度被召唤到异世界锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家现在失去 支撑世界的艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面临消失的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企图得到锡菲罗的三个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及另一个来路不明的势力 进攻锡菲罗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中之一是法连
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是法连的长公主飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小风的说服下 放弃了当锡菲罗的支柱的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞鸟公主担心我们 使用了巨大小三子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱离停泊在城堡附近的 欧多札姆的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡内的欧多札姆的伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到支柱的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展开了行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第43话 王冠的房间与支柱的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧多札姆的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图是我的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪波尼亚的束缚 好像解开了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪波尼亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听得到我的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔希欧蕾 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪波尼亚在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到这个国家本身 有迪波尼亚的邪恶之气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不管 我怎么在锡菲罗寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是找不到那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪波尼亚在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道有关迪波尼亚的事 被封印起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法连的龙好像移走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个巨大小孩也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在赶快把NSX修复
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,札兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要多久可以行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧多札姆时间的三小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以死啊 伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听兰迪斯提过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开王冠的房间的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有导师古列夫的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及兰迪斯的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫的生命资料 依然不明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好拜托兰迪斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道对方不会喜欢你 你为什么还要喜欢上他？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧多札姆的人在城内逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 百忙中打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有藏匿的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是什么了不起的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之刚好足够使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护之风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍暴龙卷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么到处都有爆炸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走的欧多札姆司令官 不是只有一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多地方同时爆炸 该去哪个地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算司令官不在那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被布置的爆炸物还是要清理的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 你回去看看好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 下面拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所决定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论遇到多少困难 都一定会付诸实行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的共通点是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无药可治的顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不能改变的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不全力对付我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死的人将会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王冠的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是 放置支柱信物的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王冠的形状在改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  能成为下一任支柱的人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 房间有魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有具备资格的人 能进入那个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要试试我有没有那个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是错的 锡菲罗是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护您的亲卫队长决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其找人保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如给锡菲罗的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护您 就等于保护锡菲罗呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗唯一 拥有魔法剑士资格的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及协助您祈导的神官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请喊我谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不在锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全感觉不到他的气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯大概有他的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就随他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要召唤魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 召唤魔法骑士的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱上了他 谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不被允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这是不被允许的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我无法控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能顺着自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您与谢加图的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 您是这世界的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 您也是一个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你祈求自已的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会有人责怪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算大家原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是无法原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明知会导致大家不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还祈求自已的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请引导我召唤的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这场战争令人心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而被卷入的魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就仰赖你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我转告魔法骑士 告诉她们 我很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以只属于你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗属于 住在这个国家的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定这个国家未来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
